text: Tinne is a Germanic female given name. Notable people with this name include: * Tinne Gilis, Belgian squash player * Tinne Hoff Kjeldsen, Danish mathematician * Tinne Kruse, Danish badminton player * Tinne Van der Straeten, Flemish politician * Tinne Vilhelmson-Silfvén, Swedish horse rider
title: Tinne (name)
